description: This common Plezier purrs with a rating of 17, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 51, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 1 for East, Stringalong for South, and 3 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [51 Votes, Common]
